Running Tests by Marker
With markers applied, you can selectively run specific groups of tests:

Run All Tests (Default):

bash
Copy code
pytest tests/
Run Smoke Tests Only:

bash
Copy code
pytest -m "smoke"
Run Regression Tests Only:

bash
Copy code
pytest -m "regression"
Run Both Smoke and Regression Tests:

bash
Copy code
pytest -m "smoke or regression"
Exclude Specific Marker (e.g., exclude smoke):

bash
Copy code
pytest -m "not smoke"